# VR Telepresence Stereoscopic Video Encoding Performance Testing

## Overview

Performance testing protocol for real-time stereoscopic video streaming from robot-mounted cameras to VR headset at 90 fps with <40ms total latency target.

**Based on:** "UHD Video Encoding in CPU Versus GPU: Quality and Performance Trade-Offs" (Salcedo-Navarro et al., 2025, IEEE Access)

**Key Difference from Reference Paper:**
- Paper: 4K (3840×2160) offline encoding at 60fps with medium preset
- This project: Real-time 90fps encoding at optimized resolutions for VR telepresence

